Alleged VBS Mutual Bank mastermind Tshifhiwa Matodzi's personal assistant, Takalani Veronica Mmbi, and her company Venmont Holdings, are facing liquidation over a R37m overdraft advanced to the company by the now defunct bank. The bank's liquidator, Anush Rooplal, is also gunning for a R50m overdraft facility that was allegedly created fraudulently by VBS for the benefit of Mmbi's company. TO READ MORE ON THIS STORY GET A COPY OF TODAY'S SUNDAY WORLD